<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-15015] Cassandra metrics documentation is not correct for Hint_delays metric</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15015</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Cassandra metrics for hint delays are not correctly referred on the documentation web page:&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/operating/metrics.html#hintsservice-metrics&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/operating/metrics.html#hintsservice-metrics&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The metrics are defined in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/06209037ea56b5a2a49615a99f1542d6ea1b2947/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/metrics/HintsServiceMetrics.java#L45-L52&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;code&lt;/a&gt;&#160;as &apos;Hint_delays&apos; and &apos;Hint_delays-&amp;lt;ip_of_peer&amp;gt;&apos; but those are listed on the website as &apos;Hints_delays&apos; and &apos;Hints_delays-&amp;lt;PeerIP&amp;gt;&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The documentation should be fixed by&#160;removing the extra &apos;s&apos; in&#160;Hints to match it with code.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Jira for adding hint_delays: &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-13234&quot; title=&quot;Add histogram for delay to deliver hints&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-13234&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-13234&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
